---

---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Beneficios</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-ink tracking-tight">
        Todo lo que necesitas para llegar a tus clientes
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-muted text-lg">
        Difunde conecta WhatsApp Business y Email en un solo lugar, con campañas, plantillas y automatizaciones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 auto-rows-fr">
      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">Campañas multicanal</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Crea y envía campañas masivas por WhatsApp y Email desde un mismo panel. Sube tu CSV, asigna variables y deja que Difunde gestione el envío con throttling inteligente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">Automatizaciones inteligentes</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Dispara respuestas automáticas por WhatsApp cuando llega un Email. Conecta canales y crea reglas sin código.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8h2a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2v4l-4-4H9a1.994 1.994 0 01-1.414-.586m0 0L11 14h4a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2v4l.586-.586z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">Chat en tiempo real</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Bandeja de conversaciones en vivo con WebSockets. Soporte para texto, imágenes, documentos y notas de voz.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">Plantillas Meta sincronizadas</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Sincroniza tus plantillas de WhatsApp aprobadas desde Meta. Extracción automática de variables y modo de prueba.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">API segura para integraciones</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Conecta tu CRM, ERP o plataforma propia mediante API Keys con autenticación y límites de tasa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal rounded-2xl border border-[oklch(0.90_0.005_0)] bg-white p-8 card-hover flex flex-col reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-ink">Auditoría con integridad</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Cada acción crítica queda registrada con hash chain criptográfico para compliance empresarial.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
